{"tid":112171,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"民航處隱瞞1月份6宗飛行間距不足安全事故 次數頻密「歷來罕有」","createTime":"2017-02-08T03:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T03:17:08.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"60da724cda9833771f6876bab38a17f48ce36cfa","tid":112171,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T03:10:23.000Z","msg":"(傳真社香港8日電) - 傳真社獲民航處消息人士確認，因新空管系統未能及時發出「預測衝突警告」(Predictive Conflict Alert) 及「衝突警告」(Conflict Alert)，今年1月份發生了至少6宗航機飛行間距不足(Loss of Separation)的安全事故，在其中5宗事故，涉事航機皆未能維持平面距離至少5浬及垂直距離至少1,000呎，違反了國際民航組織的安全標準。有資深前線空管人員向傳真社表示，一個月內發生6宗航機飛行間距不足，次數之頻密是「歷來罕有及不能接受」。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.factwire.org/single-post/2017/02/08/%E6%B0%91%E8%88%AA%E8%99%95%E9%9A%B1%E7%9E%9E1%E6%9C%88%E4%BB%BD6%E5%AE%97%E9%A3%9B%E8%A1%8C%E9%96%93%E8%B7%9D%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%85-%E6%AC%A1%E6%95%B8%E9%A0%BB%E5%AF%86%E3%80%8C%E6%AD%B7%E4%BE%86%E7%BD%95%E6%9C%89%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.factwire.org%2Fsingle-post%2F2017%2F02%2F08%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%2588%25AA%25E8%2599%2595%25E9%259A%25B1%25E7%259E%259E1%25E6%259C%2588%25E4%25BB%25BD6%25E5%25AE%2597%25E9%25A3%259B%25E8%25A1%258C%25E9%2596%2593%25E8%25B7%259D%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%25E4%25BA%258B%25E6%2595%2585-%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E6%2595%25B8%25E9%25A0%25BB%25E5%25AF%2586%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E4%25BE%2586%25E7%25BD%2595%25E6%259C%2589%25E3%2580%258D&d=%2FIqeUsS3N0qecbTP5cC9OHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=fa7c09f9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.factwire.org/single-post/2017/02/08/%E6%B0%91%E8%88%AA%E8%99%95%E9%9A%B1%E7%9E%9E1%E6%9C%88%E4%BB%BD6%E5%AE%97%E9%A3%9B%E8%A1%8C%E9%96%93%E8%B7%9D%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%85-%E6%AC%A1%E6%95%B8%E9%A0%BB%E5%AF%86%E3%80%8C%E6%AD%B7%E4%BE%86%E7%BD%95%E6%9C%89%E3%80%8D</a>"},{"pid":"7215cd130cb7fdaaaaad3ad65640719698d3403f","tid":112171,"uid":79711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime